{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/define\"><code>define()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/get\"><code>get()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/upgrade\"><code>upgrade()</code></a></li><li><em><code>whenDefined()</code></em></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  O <strong><code>whenDefined()</code></strong> é um método de <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry\"><code>CustomElementRegistry</code></a> e a interface retorna uma <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> que é resolvido quando o elemento nomeado é\n  definido.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>customElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">whenDefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> Promise<span class=\"token operator\">&lt;</span>CustomElementConstructor<span class=\"token operator\">&gt;</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"name\">name</dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>Nome do elemento personalizado.</p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_de_retorno","title":"Valor de retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p>\n  A <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Promise\"><code>Promise</code></a> que será cumprida com o <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">elemento personalizado (en-US)</a>'s construtor quando um\n  <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">custom element (en-US)</a> torna-se definido com o nome fornecido. (Se o <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/customElements\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">custom element (en-US)</a> já foi\n  definido, a promessa devolvida será imediatamente cumprida.)\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceções","title":"Exceções","isH3":true,"content":"<table>\n  <thead>\n    <tr>\n      <th>Exceção</th>\n      <th>Descrição</th>\n    </tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr>\n      <td><code>SyntaxError</code></td>\n      <td>Se o nome fornecido não for um <a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/custom-elements.html#valid-custom-element-name\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">nome de elemento personalizado válido</a>, a promessa rejeita com um <code>SyntaxError</code>.</td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":"<p>\n  Este exemplo usa <code>whenDefined()</code> para detectar quando os elementos personalizados que compõem um menu são definidos. O menu exibe o conteúdo do espaço reservado até que o conteúdo do\n  menu real esteja pronto para ser exibido.\n</p>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu-container<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>menu-placeholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Loading...<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>nav-menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item 1<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item 2<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n     ...\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Item N<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>menu-item</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav-menu</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>nav</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> container <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getElementById</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'menu-container'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> placeholder <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.menu-placeholder'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Busca todos os filhos do menu que ainda não foram definidos.</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> undefinedElements <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelectorAll</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">':not(:defined)'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">async</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">removePlaceholder</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> promises <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token operator\">...</span>undefinedElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">map</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>\n    <span class=\"token parameter\">button</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> customElements<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">whenDefined</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>button<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>localName<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// Espere que todos os filhos sejam atualizados</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">await</span> Promise<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">all</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>promises<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token comment\">// em seguida, remova o espaço reservado</span>\n  container<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">removeChild</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>placeholder<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token function\">removePlaceholder</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/custom-elements.html#dom-customelementregistry-whendefined-dev","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores","isH3":false,"query":"api.CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"compatibilidade_com_navegadores"}],"summary":"O whenDefined() é um método de CustomElementRegistry e a interface retorna uma Promise que é resolvido quando o elemento nomeado é\n  definido.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/customelementregistry/whendefined","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/customelementregistry/whendefined/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry","title":"CustomElementRegistry"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/CustomElementRegistry/whenDefined","title":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined()"}],"pageTitle":"CustomElementRegistry.whenDefined() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}